snippet.title: Bakugan: Champions of Vestroia - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Team up with your favorite Bakugan and battle your way towards becoming the Bakugan Battle League Champion when Bakugan Champions of Vestroia comes exclusively to Nintendo Switch on Nov. 3rd!

https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/bakugan-champions-of-vestroia-switch/
